<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" contentStyleType="text/css" data-diagram-type="CLASS" height="442px" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width:790px;height:442px;background:#FFFFFF;" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 790 442" width="790px" zoomAndPan="magnify"><?plantuml 1.2026.4beta2?><defs/><g><g class="legend" data-source-line="1"><rect fill="#DDDDDD" height="401.125" rx="7.5" ry="7.5" style="stroke:#000000;stroke-width:1;" width="759.376" x="12" y="22"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="399.3008" x="17" y="39.9951">The plugin you are using seems to generated a bad URL.</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="295.8867" x="17" y="56.292">This URL does not look like DEFLATE data.</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="367.6641" x="17" y="72.5889">It looks like your plugin is using HUFFMAN encoding.</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="88.8857">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="671.7061" x="17" y="105.1826">This means you have now to add an header ~1 to your data. For example, you have to change:</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="530.6875" x="17" y="121.4795">http://www.plantuml.com/plantuml/png/dVPdShtBFL6fpzj1qr0IvkExjaKxhg...</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="14.0547" x="17" y="137.7764">to</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="551.3252" x="17" y="154.0732">http://www.plantuml.com/plantuml/png/~1dVPdShtBFL6fpzj1qr0IvkExjaKxhg...</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="170.3701">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="138.2773" x="17" y="186.667">It will work this way</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="428.1484" x="17" y="202.9639">You may contact the PlantUML team at plantuml@gmail.com</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="749.376" x="17" y="219.2607">But you should also probably contact the plugin authors you are currently using and send them this image</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="235.5576">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="232.5449" x="17" y="251.8545">For the record, here is your data:</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="268.1514">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="652.3193" x="17" y="284.4482">dVPdShtBFL6fpzj1qr0IvkExjaKxhggrRBAvJuuYbLPJLLuTJlCEYkRt8KdXFfEHhdIGCqa2tLQK9mU6</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="698.5986" x="17" y="300.7451">E32LzpwxsxHsws7Od77zM2e-sxOJoLFo1kOoBTFvZ2jsVwPBfNGMGXkiqqzOwGdxM2S0QYgIRMjgpfEE</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="697.4297" x="17" y="317.042">1X2rjvvq9Kc63ZBHN4RE1K_RCoMx-W538KUPT0s0CJNnY_CGgH6WZhYKc-M5zxuf9ZaBJrAa84ZgjRXL</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="671.7539" x="17" y="333.3389">ojO8iIOVCkO6jFuyNpr4_R4mnuZp1mwUQXY-D_JyHcNoFFni7_W17J7ffu3Iq0_ysIekoEnNsup7T27u</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="689.7393" x="17" y="349.6357">qLNf8k8HKZ_rhg2Fiyupfuzfft7W8Wpna3D1e1gWc-Ro47WOtIxNgpbUo8TK03OjDi1WroQpX6CiCoNv</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="668.1992" x="17" y="365.9326">N_qISNc1RnbtkaPI7pnsb6reuTw5eHCO2dIUWBKTvGqxlFtcXJjKjrLttmD0vzXu1i8GF5eP1Cg2Rch5</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="697.2314" x="17" y="382.2295">DfKF7Dzm4dYw0gtnBa2hEcP2wlld4_tSD2T8-OGu01PHu1qfVMeSB8X8ZM6K2EpSq-cV0Zgk3BrN_Lky</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="697.8877" x="17" y="398.5264">ZmxN9uE0QSbzfDg79oMWMxb6xT1OgVkQofDErBZaCR22ijmICjlkrtoBe7MODi8oDb2_kNRi2nTAtOcA</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="151.8125" x="17" y="414.8232">dkUmdD_61yT_AA==</text></g><?plantuml-src ZLHPaweu67tdL-G7N6r1M-YkkbKZcmkR8hRB2nKXx10CYQ0FzxSFwlJScfUPUKabttBE-PPAWM9KXPoN850NB4uhSCCCG880Qz8g1Wr2PGCe1dqO8f2Y441mXY7OkUQmJqkRnms463MWmXGK6EUWI7C4L4qtPvu6GaZXa5k-NCtBrtEGRxuUuKMrsEcwDRC1gW8SzeOXzy8l4QoQfwm4Nb7FqZxqmB1NKe44mH0Hy8j_s9wmJpwWOm9G1ykwG3z-v_OnGGAh67ro2QNrvzjRsxR3ke0LPMKn373vzlrugwluBVnQXzk4ohevZUfxnb_8Q7dDjIw3HfV4m-6Ge_Z_8VtY_nlhqQGsBGhGOf83-gYzXJVksAiluGq4kA8meBq3WVK3UsUPW29O0aZ1DzaVSGdJ9pydC_gil4amA_fc5Gq6DS5dU2x-2VRN822Z2IRDtmiGC49GHVlWrtnW5VRhq1zzJlcIbvOmHXptQFO3YA00a_17FvG-FMr-p-EJu_wz_9YuykowOknuDjShqsJUgb2qO-vIoGWFUgGjad0vLovGeER6-2XtKquR2-QzRhkcMpHj8pgXADuj0GsQpbbXKyTyxc3Pqwyd8Mk-shKSsNDhViZJo-NkjFEmiuJjQ7ECbwwLnNMaQHn_44XslLu-Z60wFiaBU-9glE6x2hQwmVvzB1cxjJTgHihAhew-CeyNq_qfEHh1m7g_TopwE45vHMPGcfpYp3sO7CuSALqwNqhkJ3ETtUoQJ7ntKbRiLFDbkziSZWFLNzqMWOrrlKf5Vy-BAp6As7Xv6VctPeboh5LsmshH4qJ6NKmxad9fOPnyaiI2djvO7R5x555nB-th2evL7l7nFXYuU2Bk7RhixBW-xx3a6QEnawafloTuKn-cIgfW-yhP_cMvjGFUhSuqX-kbM5VDUKeGyzftj50S8LpkzhBXNUUNhj1fS5XbHaPCIajrTBqV69zAS_qThNab5jmWUUVKoD15zLvEmcCxYcabGo7HWhNG5aKuyUbM5JnfuCp